<h2 id="innovation" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#innovation"><span>Innovation</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>The rocking piston – GSE’s bedrock technology. Reliable and simple in design, it allows for internal adjustment for the ultimate in flexibility. The rocking piston offers an exceptionally long life in many conditions.</li>
<li>The articulated piston – these oil-less piston units are suitable for use in both compressors and vacuum pumps. Strong, reliable, low-maintenance and permanently lubricated, they can be serviced at your site.</li>
<li>The rotary lobe and screw – offering a very hygienic conditions, superb efficiency, reliability and resistance to corrosion (providing the internal parts are coated). This forms part of our offering for the fuel-cell market.</li>
<li>The diaphragm – our highly efficient flexing diaphragm (membrane) pumps are well-suited for industrial, chemical and medical/laboratory applications.
